text: Malyshi () is a rural locality (a village) in Klyapovskoye Rural Settlement, Beryozovsky District, Perm Krai, Russia. The population was 143 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == Geography == It is located on the Barda River. == References == Category:Rural localities in Beryozovsky District, Perm Krai
title: Malyshi
